target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002700_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Je ne vous apprends rien si je vous dis que c'est le seul. Le perdre condamnerait à mort vos amis.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002710_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Now, now. Try anything here and we're all likely to fall.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002710_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Du calme<var 1D /var>! Du calme<var 1D /var>! Si on se bat ici, on va tous tomber dans le vide<var 1D /var>! Je vous ai dit que je voulais négocier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002720_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Eventually, someone will come to our rescue. Or yours. Promise us safe passage and we'll give you the antidote!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002720_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>J'ai toute votre attention<var 1D /var>? Nos soldats et vos amis ne vont pas tarder à nous rejoindre. Peu importe qui arrive en premier, tout ce que je veux, c'est être secouru en priorité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002730_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Do we have a deal?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002730_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Je vous remettrai alors l'antidote. C'est un marché honnête, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002740_RANJIT<tab>We do not negotiate with the enemy. The villagers' lives are forfeit. As is yours...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002740_RANJIT<tab>Soit... Que ta vie serve à envoyer quelques rebelles de plus dans la tombe.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002750_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>General?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002750_EULMOREADJUTANT<tab>Ha<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002760_YSHTOLA<tab>Do not fail.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002760_YSHTOLA<tab>Je compte sur toi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002770_RANJIT<tab>How noble. And pointless.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002770_RANJIT<tab>Elle a plongé sans hésiter...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002780_RYNE<tab>Is─is everyone all right?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002780_RYNE<tab>Ohé<var 1D /var>! Tout le monde va bien<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002790_RYNE<tab>What in the─
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002790_RYNE<tab>Qu'est-ce que c'est que ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002800_THANCRED<tab>Urianger!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002800_THANCRED<tab>Urianger<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002810_URIANGER<tab>At once!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002810_URIANGER<tab>Oui<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002820_THANCRED<tab>Down with you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002820_THANCRED<tab>Au revoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002830_RANJIT<tab>Guh!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002830_RANJIT<tab>(cri de douleur, “Guh<var 1D /var>!”)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002840_RYNE<tab>Where...where is Y'shtola?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002840_RYNE<tab>... Et Y'shtola<var 1D /var>? Où est-elle<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002850_RYNE<tab>Runar. Thank goodness.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002850_RYNE<tab>Ouf... monsieur Runar est ici.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002860_THANCRED<tab>We delivered the antidote to Slitherbough, and from what we could gather on the way here, the Eulmorans have had the good manners to withdraw.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002860_THANCRED<tab>Serpentige a reçu un peu d'antidote, et l'ennemi s'est replié dans sa forteresse. Nous sommes tranquilles pour le moment.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002870_THANCRED<tab>Thank the gods they did, or we would never have made it here in time. I'm told we have Runar and his comrades to thank for keeping the soldiers occupied prior to their retreat.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002870_THANCRED<tab>Il paraît que malgré les effets du poison, Runar a serré les dents et s'est battu comme un lion pour gagner autant de temps que possible...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002880_THANCRED<tab>They were preparing to come for you and Y'shtola, it seems, when Runar rallied the villagers and pursued them out of Slitherbough.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002880_THANCRED<tab>Et même avec l'armée eulmorienne loin de son hameau, il s'inquiétait pour nous et les autres. Heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment qu'il était entre de bonnes mains...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002890_RUNAR<tab>I must...I-I must...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002890_RUNAR<tab>Hmm... Hngg...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002900_RUNAR<tab>Where...am I?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002900_RUNAR<tab>Où... Où suis-je<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002910_URIANGER<tab>Yx'Maja, in the care of the Viis. Thou art safe now, friend. Pray, rest thee awhile longer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002910_URIANGER<tab>Vous êtes en sécurité à Yx'Maja. N'ayez aucune crainte.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002920_RUNAR<tab>No...no, I am all right. Somewhat heavy of limb, perhaps, but otherwise well I assure you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002920_RUNAR<tab>Ça devrait aller... Je me suis déjà porté mieux, mais au moins, je peux bouger.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002930_RUNAR<tab>I am glad to see you are all safe. When we realized where the soldiers were headed, we knew something had to be done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002930_RUNAR<tab>Je suis soulagé qu'il ne vous soit rien arrivé. Quand j'ai vu les Eulmoriens partir dans votre direction, je me suis dit qu'on devait les arrêter.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002940_RUNAR<tab>I...do not see Master Matoya. She was with you, yes? What happened to her?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002940_RUNAR<tab>... Hmm<var 1D /var>? Matoya n'est pas avec vous<var 1D /var>? Il me semblait pourtant que si...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous à Runar<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I cannot say for certain─but it was she who secured the antidote.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Elle a obtenu l'antidote, au péril de sa vie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>She saved the Night's Blessed─albeit at a cost...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>C'est grâce à elle que le peuple de la Nuit a survécu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A5_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002950_RUNAR<tab>Spare me your riddles and speak plain! Where is Master Matoya!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002950_RUNAR<tab>Qu'est-ce que ça veut dire<var 1D /var>!? Dites-moi ce qui s'est passé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002960_RUNAR<tab>Well!? Say something! Where is Master Matoya!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002960_RUNAR<tab>Quoi...<var 1D /var>!? Pourquoi vous ne dites rien<var 1D /var>? Parlez<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002970_RUNAR<tab>No...no... No, that cannot be...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002970_RUNAR<tab>C'est... C'est impossible<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002980_RUNAR<tab>Why would she do such a thing?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002980_RUNAR<tab>Ça n'a aucun sens<var 1D /var>! Matoya... Comment...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002990_RUNAR<tab>Was there no other way? I...I cannot believe that she...that she...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_002990_RUNAR<tab>Comment une simple chute pourrait-elle avoir raison de quelqu'un d'aussi incroyable<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003000_RUNAR<tab>We must begin the search immediately! I will come with you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003000_RUNAR<tab>Attendez, vous allez partir à sa recherche, non<var 1D /var>? Emmenez-moi<var 1D /var>! Laissez-moi venir avec vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003010_RUNAR<tab>What are you waiting for? We must find her! She could be trapped or hurt or...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003010_RUNAR<tab>Bah quoi<var 1D /var>? Allons-y<var 1D /var>! Matoya... Si on ne se dépêche pas...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003020_RUNAR<tab>She is alive. She is <var 1A 02 /var>alive<var 1A 01 /var>, damn you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003020_RUNAR<tab>Matoya... Elle ne peut pas... Elle ne peut pas disparaître comme ça<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003030_ALMET<tab>Forgive me for interrupting, but our scouts have apprehended an intruder.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003030_ALMET<tab>Désolée de vous déranger dans un tel moment. Nos sentinelles ont capturé un intrus.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003040_ALMET<tab>We thought perhaps he might be an associate of yours...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003040_ALMET<tab>Comme nous ne savons pas qui sont vos alliés ou vos ennemis, je vous l'ai amené.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003050_THANCRED<tab>Oh, look who it is.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003050_THANCRED<tab>Emet-Selch<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003060_EMETSELCH<tab>Well...this is embarrassing. In my defense, they are surprisingly tenacious.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003060_EMETSELCH<tab>Que voulez-vous... J'ai peut-être sous-estimé les chasseuses de la région. Elles ne laissent aucune chance à leur proie.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003070_EMETSELCH<tab>So─what trouble have you gotten yourselves into this time?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003070_EMETSELCH<tab>Et vous<var 1D /var>? Ça ne respire pas exactement la joie, ici...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003080_EMETSELCH<tab>Well, well. What an intriguing turn of events.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003080_EMETSELCH<tab>Hum hum... J'avoue vous avoir vu pénétrer dans les ruines, mais j'ignorais ce qu'il s'était passé à l'intérieur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003090_EMETSELCH<tab>My condolences, by the way. 'Tis never easy to lose the ones we love.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003090_EMETSELCH<tab>Mes condoléances pour votre amie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003100_EMETSELCH<tab>Well, she is dead, isn't she? Wishing it were otherwise will not make it so.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003100_EMETSELCH<tab>... Quoi<var 1D /var>? Elle est morte, non<var 1D /var>? Nier la vérité ne la fera pas revenir.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003110_THANCRED<tab>That <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var> should be indifferent to her loss is no surprise. But to us, she was a friend. The best of friends.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003110_THANCRED<tab>Con<var 16 /var>trai<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment à vous autres, la vie a une certaine valeur à nos yeux. Y'shtola était l'une des nôtres, et sa disparition nous affecte plus que vous ne pouvez l'imaginer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003120_RYNE<tab>You have something on your mind. What is it?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003120_RYNE<tab>Ça va<var 1D /var>? Vous pourriez peut-être faire une petite pause si vous êtes fatigué<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous à Minfilia<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'm beginning to wonder what really happened when she fell.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A6_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Je me demande juste si la chute a été fatale...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>After she fell, there was a powerful gust of wind as if from nowhere...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A6_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>J'ai ressenti un courant d'air après sa chute...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003130_URIANGER<tab>Pray recount to us again that which thou witnessed in the ruins, omitting not the slightest detail.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003130_URIANGER<tab>Vous ne voudriez pas nous expliquer à nouveau, en nous donnant autant de détails que possible<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003140_THANCRED<tab>Flow...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003140_THANCRED<tab>... La “Téléportation ancienne”<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003150_THANCRED<tab>The teleportation magick she used to spirit us away from Ul'dah after the bloody banquet! I recall a similar gale in the tunnel before it took effect.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003150_THANCRED<tab>Vous savez, c'est ce sort qui ne nécessite aucune incantation<var 1D /var>! Il y avait aussi un fort courant d'air la dernière fois que j'ai été témoin de son utilisation.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003160_EMETSELCH<tab>Interesting. I thought I sensed a brief disturbance in the Lifestream. How reassuring to know it was not my imagination.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003160_EMETSELCH<tab>Je comprends mieux... Il n'y a pas longtemps, j'ai cru sentir l'éther vaciller. C'était sûrement ça, je n'ai pas rêvé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003170_EMETSELCH<tab>I felt it only once, I should mention. Which would suggest she is still adrift on its currents.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003170_EMETSELCH<tab>Oui, enfin ce n'est arrivé qu'une fois, donc elle est peut-être entrée, et pas encore sortie du flux éthéré<var 1D /var>! Qu'est-ce qui nous dit qu'elle n'est pas en train d'y errer<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003180_URIANGER<tab>Then I fear she may yet be lost to us─for it was only by the grace of the elementals that she was plucked from that great aetherial river.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003180_URIANGER<tab>Le problème sera épineux si c'est le cas. La dernière fois que c'est arrivé, nous avons fait appel à Kan-E-Senna pour l'en extirper...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003190_EMETSELCH<tab>Oh...very well. I'll go and fetch her...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003190_EMETSELCH<tab>Hum... Je ne peux pas dire que ça m'enchante, mais voudriez-vous que je m'en occupe<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003200_EMETSELCH<tab>Perhaps a clear and unambiguous act of kindness will serve to win the trust you seem so determined to deny me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003200_EMETSELCH<tab>Puisque vous n'accordez que peu de crédit à mes paroles, voilà une chance de prouver par mes actes que je ne suis pas votre ennemi.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003210_EMETSELCH<tab>Yes, this place should serve well enough.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003210_EMETSELCH<tab>Cet endroit devrait faire l'affaire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003220_EMETSELCH<tab>Might I have a little space? I <var 1A 02 /var>need<var 1A 01 /var> to concentrate.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003220_EMETSELCH<tab>Beau travail, l'ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, mais aurais-tu l'obligeance de t'écarter maintenant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003230_EMETSELCH<tab>Now then...what color was her soul again?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003230_EMETSELCH<tab>Bien... De quelle couleur était son âme, déjà<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003240_EMETSELCH<tab>Ah... There you are.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003240_EMETSELCH<tab>Ah... Trouvée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003250_RUNAR<tab>He─He's done it! He's brought her back!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003250_RUNAR<tab>C'est bien elle<var 1D /var>! Matoya<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003260_YSHTOLA<tab>(WAKING UP REAX)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003260_YSHTOLA<tab>(Gémit doucement)

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003270_THANCRED<tab>Y'shtola, are you all right?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003270_THANCRED<tab>Comment te sens-tu<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003280_YSHTOLA<tab>Yes... Though I cannot imagine how. What happened?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003280_YSHTOLA<tab>Ça a déjà été mieux... Que m'est-il arrivé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003290_URIANGER<tab>Thou didst invoke the power of Flow, which thence did usher thy soul unto the Lifestream.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003290_URIANGER<tab>Tu as été arrachée une deuxième fois au flux éthéré. Tu te souviens y être entrée après avoir eu recours à la Téléportation ancienne<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003300_YSHTOLA<tab>I wanted to save the antidote, and after that...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003300_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui, je me rappelle maintenant. Je voulais récupérer cette fiole. C'était le seul moyen d'obtenir le remède...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003310_YSHTOLA<tab>(SUDDEN LAUGH)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003310_YSHTOLA<tab>Ha ha... Ha ha ha...<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003320_YSHTOLA<tab>I did something exceedingly reckless. For which you will just have to forgive me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003320_YSHTOLA<tab>Faites ce que je dis, pas ce que je fais<var 1D /var>! Merci à tous d'avoir élucidé ma disparition...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003330_YSHTOLA<tab>(SHOCK REAX)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003330_YSHTOLA<tab>Ah<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003340_RUNAR<tab>Master Matoya! Oh, thank the heavens you're all right!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003340_RUNAR<tab>Matoya<var 1D /var>! Matoya<var 1D /var>!!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003350_RUNAR<tab>I had nearly given up hope.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003350_RUNAR<tab>Vous êtes vivante... Vivante<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003360_YSHTOLA<tab>Please, Runar, dry your tears. What would the others think if they saw you like this?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003360_YSHTOLA<tab>Sèche tes larmes, mon enfant. Tu vas faire pleurer tout le monde.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003370_YSHTOLA<tab>Come now─did you really think I would go gently into that dark night with so much left undone? So many mysteries left unsolved?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003370_YSHTOLA<tab>Quel genre de mage serais-je si je me laissais vaincre si facilement<var 1D /var>? Je ne quitterai pas ce monde tant que je n'aurai pas les réponses à mes nombreuses questions<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003380_EMETSELCH<tab>Ahem. Is there aught you wish to say to me? A word of <var 1A 02 /var>thanks<var 1A 01 /var>, perhaps?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003380_EMETSELCH<tab>Daignera-t-on seulement accorder un petit mot de re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ment à celui qui a rendu ces retrouvailles possibles<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003390_URIANGER<tab>Emet-Selch, the Ascian of whom I spoke. 'Twas he who plucked thee from the Lifestream.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003390_URIANGER<tab>Voici Emet-Selch, un Ascien... C'est lui qui vous a extraite du flux éthéré.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003400_YSHTOLA<tab>I see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003400_YSHTOLA<tab>J'ai beaucoup entendu parler de toi...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003410_YSHTOLA<tab>Thank you. Differences notwithstanding, you saved my life, and for that I am grateful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003410_YSHTOLA<tab>Je n'irais pas jusqu'à te promettre une confiance aveugle, mais je te suis re<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>sante de m'avoir sauvée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003420_YSHTOLA<tab>But let us turn our attention to more important matters, such as the Qitana Ravel.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003420_YSHTOLA<tab>Au fait, j'espère que vous n'êtes pas déjà allés à l'Enchevêtrement des Qitari<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003430_YSHTOLA<tab>You had better not have explored its depths without me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003430_YSHTOLA<tab>Si vous avez osé visiter des ruines anciennes sans moi, je ne vous le pardonnerai jamais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous à Y'shtola<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Heavens no. In fact, I was awaiting your return.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Bien sûr que non<var 1D /var>! On attend quoi pour s'y rendre du coup<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>I wouldn't have known where to start.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>Nous comptons bien trop sur toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>I'll tell you after you've got some rest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A7_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Arrête un peu tes bêtises...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003440_THANCRED<tab>Well. Almet and the others should be pleased to see you in such <var 1A 02 /var>uncharacteristically<var 1A 01 /var> high spirits. Let us return to Fanow, then, and discuss the coming expedition.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003440_THANCRED<tab>Almet et les autres seront rassurées de te voir sur pied. Retournons à Fanow, nous pourrons y parler de l'Enchevêtrement des Qitari.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003450_RYNE<tab>The Lightwarden is dead. The Blessed's prayers have been answered...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003450_RYNE<tab>C'était le troisième... Je me demande si le peuple de la Nuit est lui aussi en train d'admirer le ciel étoilé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003460_THANCRED<tab>Aye, that they have.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003460_THANCRED<tab>Je pense que oui...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003470_URIANGER<tab>His condition yet troubleth thee?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003470_URIANGER<tab>Tu t'inquiètes pour lui<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003480_URIANGER<tab>Her condition yet troubleth thee?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003480_URIANGER<tab>Tu t'inquiètes pour elle<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003490_YSHTOLA<tab>It does. Though <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> shows no immediate signs of corruption, the danger remains. <var 08 E905 ((She)) ((He)) /var> must be told.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003490_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui... Tout s'est bien passé cette fois encore, mais qu'en sera-t-il à l'avenir<var 1D /var>? Je ne compte pas lui cacher plus longtemps la vérité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003500_YSHTOLA<tab>...Would you describe it to me, Urianger? Paint for me a picture with your words.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003500_YSHTOLA<tab>Dis, Urianger... Comment est la nuit<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003510_URIANGER<tab>A sea of shimmering stars. Diamonds strewn across a raven gown, boundless and beautiful.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003510_URIANGER<tab>Elle est telle une étoffe de velours noir ébène dans laquelle auraient été tissées des étoiles. Et leurs teintes blanches et irisées décorent ce canevas de leurs myriades.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003520_URIANGER<tab>'Tis an exquisite sight not unlike that of the Source. Calm and gentle...and forgiving...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003520_URIANGER<tab>Cette nuit ressemble en tout point à celle de notre monde. Magnifique, douce, paisible... La même étendue céleste, la même mer sombre dans laquelle on voudrait plonger.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003530_YSHTOLA<tab>I can see it...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003530_YSHTOLA<tab>Tant mieux...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003540_URIANGER<tab>For however deep the void, or wide the expanse, there is no shore so distant as to be beyond the reach of light. ...Ominous though that may sound, given our present travails.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003540_URIANGER<tab>Les étoiles sont elles aussi porteuses d'un flux vital. La vue de ce spectacle doit être majestueuse, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003550_YSHTOLA<tab>Well fought. Let us return home.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003550_YSHTOLA<tab>Bien joué<var 1D /var>! On va pouvoir rentrer la tête haute.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003560_YSHTOLA<tab>The murals. If I am not mistaken, they predate the empire.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003560_YSHTOLA<tab>Les fresques sur ces murs datent de l'époque de Ronka, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003570_RYNE<tab>How can you tell?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003570_RYNE<tab>Vous pouvez les voir<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003580_YSHTOLA<tab>A peculiarity of the paint. Most are made from mineral-based pigments, but whatever was used here is older than anything I have ever seen.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003580_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui. La plupart des pigments qui ont servi à les peindre sont composés de minéraux que je parviens à discerner.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003590_YSHTOLA<tab>According to Almet, this sanctuary was built to preserve the wisdom of the ancients. What events do these murals commemorate, I wonder?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003590_YSHTOLA<tab>Almet et les autres m'ont expliqué que l'Enchevêtrement des Qitari était autrefois un lieu sacré où était conservé un savoir ancestral. J'imagine qu'elles voulaient parler de ces fresques...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003600_EMETSELCH<tab>Must you always linger after defeating your enemies? Navigating these halls on foot is exhausting.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003600_EMETSELCH<tab>Et si on évitait les arrêts inutiles<var 1D /var>? Vous étiez tellement en retard qu'il a fallu que je vienne vous chercher. J'en ai plein les pieds<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003610_THANCRED<tab>Come to lead us to safety, have you?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003610_THANCRED<tab>Parce que tu es venu nous rac<var 16 /var>com<var 16 /var>pag<var 16 /var>ner, peut-être<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003620_EMETSELCH<tab>Hmph! I was <var 1A 02 /var>bored<var 1A 01 /var>. But how is the hero of the hour?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003620_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous rac<var 16 /var>com<var 16 /var>pag<var 16 /var>ner<var 1D /var>? Et puis quoi encore<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003630_EMETSELCH<tab>Hmm. Fighting fit, I see. Keep up the good work.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003630_EMETSELCH<tab>Hum... J'imagine qu'il faudra encore terrasser quelques bestioles pour être fixé.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003640_YSHTOLA<tab>You're plotting something.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003640_YSHTOLA<tab>C'est-à-dire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003650_EMETSELCH<tab>Every hour of every day. But never you mind about that. As I have told you a thousand times before: I like to watch. Nothing more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003650_EMETSELCH<tab>N'arrêterez-vous donc jamais de me demander de me justifier<var 1D /var>? J'ai tenu et tiens toujours ma parole<var 1D /var>: je vous aide et je vous observe.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003660_EMETSELCH<tab>Well! I would quit this place, and I suggest you do the same. There is yet work to be done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003660_EMETSELCH<tab>Et puisque j'ai vu ce que j'avais à voir, je vais pouvoir rentrer<var 1D /var>! Je vous conseille d'en faire autant. Vous avez encore pas mal de pain sur la planche.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003670_EMETSELCH<tab>Ah...there is a sight to bring a tear to the eye.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003670_EMETSELCH<tab>Voilà qui en inspire, de la mélancolie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003680_RYNE<tab>You recognize these scenes?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003680_RYNE<tab>Vous connaissez cette fresque<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003690_EMETSELCH<tab>That I do. Indeed, there was a time when anyone and everyone would.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003690_EMETSELCH<tab>Il fut un temps où personne n'en ignorait l'existence.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003700_EMETSELCH<tab>Until one calamitous day when the world was divided across ten and three reflections, sundering the land and all who dwelled upon it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003700_EMETSELCH<tab>Lorsque le monde éclata, il se divisa en un monde primitif et treize reflets. Il en alla de même pour chaque vie, qui fut fragmentée et dispersée dans chaque reflet, pour y forger un nouveau destin.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003710_EMETSELCH<tab>And the worst part? No one could remember it. Not really. Just fragments and fleeting memories of an achingly familiar world...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003710_EMETSELCH<tab>Ces quatorze fragments d'une même âme vécurent sans aucun souvenir du monde originel, même s'il arrivait qu'une brève vision de celui-ci vienne hanter leurs rêves...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003720_EMETSELCH<tab>A vision shared of a paradise lost, preserved only in song and scripture and paint...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003720_EMETSELCH<tab>Un rêve commun au genre humain tout entier... Il le connaissait, sans le reconnaître pour autant. Il fit de ce grand mystère l'objet de dessins, de chansons et de bien d'autres choses...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003730_EMETSELCH<tab>Once upon a time. Yet here we find ourselves again. To look, learn, and <var 1A 02 /var>remember<var 1A 01 /var>...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003730_EMETSELCH<tab>Ça faisait un moment que je n'avais plus vu une de ces fresques. Jamais je n'aurais imaginé en trouver une ici.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003740_YSHTOLA<tab>Then share with us the stories you know so well. We are listening.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003740_YSHTOLA<tab>Puisque tu en sais autant, tu peux peut-être nous en dire plus<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003750_EMETSELCH<tab>Before the great sundering, there was one world. A world that knew naught but peace and prosperity.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003750_EMETSELCH<tab>C'était avant l'éclatement du monde originel. À l'époque, l'endroit était peuplé par les nombreux habitants d'une civilisation prospère.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003760_EMETSELCH<tab>Until it was faced with a crisis. Unprecedented, terrifying. Civilization found itself perched upon a precipice, staring into oblivion.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003760_EMETSELCH<tab>Mais l'ordre des choses périclita et une calamité sans précédent se produisit, menaçant la vie et la planète tout entière.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003770_EMETSELCH<tab>But through prayer and sacrifice, the will of the star was made manifest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003770_EMETSELCH<tab>À force de prières et de sacrifices, cette civilisation tissa un nouvel ordre naturel pour sa planète... La volonté de l'astre était née.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003780_EMETSELCH<tab>Zodiark was His name, and by His grace was the calamity averted.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003780_EMETSELCH<tab>“Zordiarche” vit le jour. Et grâce à lui, la calamité fut maîtrisée.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003790_YSHTOLA<tab>Zodiark!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003790_YSHTOLA<tab>Qu'est-ce que Zordiarche vient faire là-dedans<var 1D /var>? Qu'est-ce que ça veut dire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003800_EMETSELCH<tab>A savior mighty and magnificent, deserving of reverence and gratitude...one would have thought. Yet some thought otherwise.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003800_EMETSELCH<tab>La calamité passa, mais Zordiarche et son incommensurable puissance divisaient les hommes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003810_EMETSELCH<tab>From the fears of these naysayers would rise Hydaelyn─She who was to serve as His shackles. To bind Him and hold Him in check.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003810_EMETSELCH<tab>Certains pensaient qu'il valait mieux le confiner, et donnèrent naissance à Hydaelyn, afin de l'entraver.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003820_EMETSELCH<tab>And so they fought, and they fought, and they fought. And in the end...Hydaelyn was victorious.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003820_EMETSELCH<tab>Le combat fit rage, et Hydaelyn ne triompha que de justesse.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003830_EMETSELCH<tab>With all Her strength She smote Him─dealing a blow so devastating that it split the very fabric of reality. And thus was Zodiark banished and His being divided.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003830_EMETSELCH<tab>L'assaut qu'elle mena de tout son corps brisa le monde... et fractionna Zordiarche qui se retrouva emprisonné.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003840_EMETSELCH<tab>That concludes today's lesson on long-forgotten history. Though I imagine your Mother would offer a rather contradictory account. As is Her wont.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003840_EMETSELCH<tab>Voilà pour l'histoire oubliée de tous. Libre à vous d'y croire ou non. Je sais bien qu'Hydaelyn a un tout autre son de cloche.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003850_THANCRED<tab>I'm sorry─I can only assume I misheard, but it sounded an awful lot like you were implying both Zodiark and Hydaelyn are not gods, but─
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003850_THANCRED<tab>Admettons... Admettons que tu dises vrai. Ça changerait com<var 16 /var>plè<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment l'essence de ce que sont Zordiarche et Hydaelyn<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003860_EMETSELCH<tab>What? Not gods of the First? Is that what you thought these paintings depicted? Or...? Oh! Ohhh...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003860_EMETSELCH<tab>Parce que vous n'aviez toujours pas réalisé<var 1D /var>? Ces deux entités n'ont jamais été les dieux primitifs de cette étoile.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003870_EMETSELCH<tab>They are gods after a fashion, yes, but no different from the kind with which you are so intimately acquainted. Formed of faith and prayer, of conviction and devotion...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003870_EMETSELCH<tab>Ce sont des volontés de l'astre matérialisées par l'Homme. Vous préférez que j'utilise des termes plus simples<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003880_EMETSELCH<tab>The eldest and most powerful...of primals.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003880_EMETSELCH<tab>Ce sont les plus anciens et les plus puissants des Primordiaux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003890_YSHTOLA<tab>You have spun quite a tale.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003890_YSHTOLA<tab>Je comprends ce que tu dis, mais j'ai beaucoup de mal à y croire...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003900_YSHTOLA<tab>Yet you have not explained the role of the Ascians in all of this. How is it you are privy to ancient secrets lost to time?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003900_YSHTOLA<tab>Et qui es-tu, toi, pour détenir une telle vérité<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003901_EMETSELCH<tab>(LAUGH)
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003901_EMETSELCH<tab>Ha ha ha...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003910_EMETSELCH<tab>Finally, <var 1A 02 /var>finally<var 1A 01 /var>, you ask the right question! And shrewd questions warrant honest answers...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003910_EMETSELCH<tab>Enfin, j'ai cru que vous ne le demanderiez jamais<var 1D /var>! C'est vrai, ça... Qu'est-ce qu'un Ascien<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003920_EMETSELCH<tab>We Ascians know because it is our history. Our story.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003920_EMETSELCH<tab>En ce qui me concerne, je suis un Ascien originel... Car il se trouve que nous ne sommes pas tous les mêmes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003930_EMETSELCH<tab>It was we who summoned Zodiark─we natives of that sundered paradise.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003930_EMETSELCH<tab>Les miens sont ceux qui ont invoqué Zordiarche. En d'autres termes, nous sommes les humains qui peuplaient le monde avant qu'il n'éclate.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003940_EMETSELCH<tab>Now do you see why we yearn for the Great Rejoining?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003940_EMETSELCH<tab>Vous comprenez sans doute mieux pourquoi la réunification des mondes est si importante à nos yeux<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003950_EMETSELCH<tab>For our world...for our people...for all creation to be made whole again.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003950_EMETSELCH<tab>Je voudrais seulement... que les Hommes retrouvent leur véritable forme.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003960_EMETSELCH<tab>Wouldn't you wish for the same?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003960_EMETSELCH<tab>Est-ce si difficile à comprendre<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003970_RUNAR<tab>Ah, you are returned! And none the worse for wear, I see.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003970_RUNAR<tab>Vous revoilà... Et sains et saufs qui plus est<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003980_YSHTOLA<tab>You needn't worry about us. What became of the Eulmoran soldiers, more importantly?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003980_YSHTOLA<tab>Oui, évidemment<var 1D /var>! Nous étions bien plus inquiets pour vous que pour nous.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003990_RUNAR<tab>They turned tail and fled at the sight of the night sky.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_003990_RUNAR<tab>Fallait pas. L'armée eulmorienne a battu en retraite dès qu'elle a vu le ciel changer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004000_RUNAR<tab>The Children of the Everlasting Dark have also retreated back to Woven Oath.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004000_RUNAR<tab>Et les enfants des Ténèbres éternelles sont allés se cacher au fond de leur trou. Ils ne peuvent plus dire que nos prières sont inutiles maintenant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004010_RUNAR<tab>Try as they might, they could not deny the truth of their own eyes...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004010_RUNAR<tab>Comment pourraient-ils nier ce dont nous avons tous été témoins<var 1D /var>? Il existe bel et bien une mer sombre dans les cieux. Un endroit où la vie va se réfugier...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004020_RUNAR<tab>The sunless sea of heaven, full of love and grace, where none need know pain or suffering.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004020_RUNAR<tab>Que cette mer remplisse nos êtres de son doux silence et d'un chaleureux amour... Là-bas, il n'y a plus de douleur ni de peur.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004030_RUNAR<tab>In that moment, when the sky's light began to wane, I knew our prayers had been answered.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004030_RUNAR<tab>Nos prières ont été entendues. Quand je m'en suis aperçu, je me suis senti déborder de bravoure.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004040_RUNAR<tab>...That we were doomed to face oblivion at life's end no longer.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004040_RUNAR<tab>La vie humaine ne s'éteindra pas si facilement, même dans ce monde en ruines.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004050_RUNAR<tab>When first we met, I harbored certain suspicions about you. Now I see that I was right.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004050_RUNAR<tab>J'ai toujours trouvé que vous et vos amis aviez quelque chose d'intrigant... Les événements récents m'ont ouvert les yeux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004060_RUNAR<tab>You are the Bringers of Shadow. The Warriors of Darkness. The saviors for whom we have prayed for so long.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004060_RUNAR<tab>J'ai face à moi les Guerriers des Ténèbres, je me trompe<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004070_YSHTOLA<tab>I suppose you're not entirely wrong...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004070_YSHTOLA<tab>Andouille, va... Est-ce si important que ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004080_YSHTOLA<tab>But we are not worthy of your reverence, nor have we any desire to be worshipped. If you would pray, pray for your children, that they may one day know a better world.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004080_YSHTOLA<tab>Les prières du peuple de la Nuit ne célèbrent rien ni personne. Elles portent la sagesse et le désir de vivre que vous avez hérité de vos ancêtres et que vous transmettrez aux générations suivantes.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004090_RUNAR<tab>...I will do as you say. But please, let us at least hold a feast to celebrate your victory. You deserve that much.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004090_RUNAR<tab>Je... Je sais. Mais vous ne voudriez pas que j'organise une fête pour vous, pour qu'on vous rende quand même un peu hommage<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004100_YSHTOLA<tab>I am sorry, Runar, but there is still much to be done, and scant time in which to do it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004100_YSHTOLA<tab>Runar... Ne retenons pas nos amis plus longtemps. Le devoir les attend.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004110_YSHTOLA<tab>We must go─all of us. For we share the same path and the same fate.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004110_YSHTOLA<tab>D'ailleurs, je ne vais pas pouvoir rester, moi non plus. Mon destin est de les accompagner.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004120_RUNAR<tab>So be it. I ask only that you hold us in your hearts, as we will hold you in ours, now and ever after. By the boundless dark, this I swear.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004120_RUNAR<tab>D'accord... Mais jamais je n'oublierai ce qu'on vous doit. Je le jure sur les Ténèbres et leur splendeur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004130_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>So there's a light sealed inside you, is there? You wouldn't know it from the outside. You look the same as you ever did to me.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004130_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Alors comme ça, la Lumière que ton corps absorbe en reste prisonnière<var 1D /var>? Tu n'as pourtant pas l'air d'aller plus mal que d'habitude.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_Q8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Que répondez-vous à Ardbert<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>I must stay the course. For the others.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_001_NONE_VOICE<tab>Mes compagnons sauront m'aider.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>And what if that changes? What if it overwhelms me?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_002_NONE_VOICE<tab>J'ai peur qu'elle me submerge...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Then I suppose there's naught to do but rest.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_A8_000_003_NONE_VOICE<tab>Rien ne sert de se torturer avec ça. Je préfère me reposer.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004140_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>True enough. Packing up and going home isn't really an option, is it. If you don't face the music here, it'll only come and find you there.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004140_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>J'espère... Surtout que le problème ne disparaîtra pas demain, même si tu arrêtes de chasser les purgateurs.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004150_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Damned if I know. It's not as if I can lift a finger to help myself, much less you.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004150_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>J'espère que tu ne comptes pas trop sur moi<var 1D /var>! Dans mon état, je suis com<var 16 /var>plè<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment impuissant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004160_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Have faith in your friends. Look out for them, and hope that they look out for you. What more can you do?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004160_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Je pense que... tu sais... tu ferais bien de t'en remettre à tes compagnons et de prendre soin d'eux. Ils comprennent la situation. Tu n'as pas vraiment le choix de toute façon, si<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004170_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Ah, yes. If they're not asking you to fight they're telling you to rest. Which isn't to say they're wrong. You'll need your strength for what's to come.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004170_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Tu as raison de prendre soin de toi. Moi aussi je trouve que manger, dormir... c'est important.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004180_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>...Think he was telling the truth? Emet, I mean. All that rot about Hydaelyn being no different from any other primal...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004180_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Au fait, je repensais à Emet-Selch et à cette histoire d'Hydaelyn créée par les Asciens.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004190_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>If so, what would that make Her “blessing”? Are we just slaves to Her will?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004190_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Si ce qu'il dit est vrai, ça veut dire que les gens comme nous, ceux qui ont reçu la bénédiction de la Lumière, ne seraient rien de plus que des subjugués<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004200_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Ahh─let's pay him no mind. Lies are the Ascians' stock-in-trade.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004200_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Bah, laisse tomber... Si tu n'y as jamais réfléchi, je veux pas t'embêter avec ça. Surtout qu'il est possible que ce type ait menti pour mieux vous manipuler.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004210_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Villains, heroes─all a matter of perspective, they'd have you believe. One man's fond memory another's waking nightmare...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004210_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Notre vision de ce qui est juste change si facilement... Un acte ayant suscité l'admiration de certaines personnes un jour, peut inspirer la haine le lendemain, au point de vouloir l'effacer de toutes les mémoires.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004220_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Me, I'm no saint or savior─just another sinner. And I know damn well I'm in no position to judge...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004220_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>C'est pour ça que je m'étais juré de ne plus encourager ni combattre qui que ce soit...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004230_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>When I saw the people of Slitherbough look up at the sky and celebrate the return of the dark...felt good.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004230_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Et puis j'ai vu l'émotion sincère des habitants de Serpentige découvrant le ciel nocturne de leurs légendes. J'ai été heureux pour eux.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004240_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>It was moments like that that I cherished─much more than the thrill of adventure. The quiet after the storm.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004240_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>L'aventure était belle, mais les re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ments reçus après le combat étaient au moins aussi plaisants.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004250_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>I always took comfort in that.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004250_WARRIOROFDARKNESS<tab>Ça m'a un peu rappelé le bon vieux temps...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004260_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Meanwhile, in Garlemald...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004260_SYSTEM_NONE_VOICE<tab>Pendant ce temps, dans le monde primitif, à Garlemald

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004270_ESTINIEN<tab>What did the scouts have to report?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004270_ESTINIEN<tab>Alors, où en sommes-nous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004280_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Several skirmishes, but nothing of consequence. The fighting seems to have taken its toll on both sides.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004280_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Aucun coup de théâtre en vue... Des petits conflits ont éclaté, mais l'armée impériale et celle de l'Alliance ne savent plus comment poursuivre l'attaque.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004290_ESTINIEN<tab>A stalemate, then. The Alliance has done well to hold the line for so long.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004290_ESTINIEN<tab>Le conflit s'enlise... Ceci dit, l'Alliance ne s'en sort pas trop mal malgré son désavantage numérique.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004300_ESTINIEN<tab>...But then they did have Ishgardian reinforcements.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004300_ESTINIEN<tab>Normal, quand on compte les soldats de la Guerre du chant des dragons dans ses rangs. Sans eux, ce ne serait cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment pas la même histoire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004310_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Nevertheless, neither side has any appetite for a prolonged engagement.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004310_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Toujours est-il qu'aucun des deux camps ne souhaite voir les combats s'éterniser.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004320_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>'Tis but the calm before the storm. And should the Empire choose to bring their full might to bear...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004320_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Cette situation, c'est le calme avant la tempête. Et s'il prenait à l'Empire l'envie de faire le ménage...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004330_ESTINIEN<tab>To say nothing of Black Rose.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004330_ESTINIEN<tab>... Il pourrait avoir recours à la rose noire.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004340_ESTINIEN<tab>All the more reason to hasten our search. How close are your people to identifying our next target?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004340_ESTINIEN<tab>Il faut accélérer les recherches. Où en sont les préparatifs pour notre in<var 16 /var>fil<var 16 /var>tra<var 16 /var>tion<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004350_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Close enough. Though I have received some troubling intelligence.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004350_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Les choses avancent, évidemment, mais on m'a rapporté d'autres nouvelles quelque peu in<var 16 /var>quié<var 16 /var>tan<var 16 /var>tes...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004360_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>One of our generals posted to the Ala Mhigan front recently disappeared without trace from the battlefield at the Ghimlyt Dark.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004360_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Un centurio de la zone frontalière de Ghimlyt a disparu.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004370_ESTINIEN<tab>Odd. Dead seems unlikely, fled less so. I wonder where he'll turn up...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004370_ESTINIEN<tab>Soit il a déserté, soit son cadavre gît quelque part... En quoi est-ce si alarmant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004380_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Were I a betting man, I would say <var 1A 02 /var>here<var 1A 01 /var>─in the capital.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004380_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Si on avait définitivement perdu sa trace, ça ne le serait cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment pas, mais il se trouve qu'on l'a aperçu récemment dans la capitale. Et ça, ça change tout...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004390_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Not that any deserter who valued his life would contemplate returning. But a corpse might, given the right encouragement.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004390_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>S'il avait fui, jamais il n'aurait osé remettre les pieds ici. Et s'il était mort... ça voudrait dire qu'il a ressuscité.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004400_ESTINIEN<tab>In the manner of His Royal Remains, you mean?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004400_ESTINIEN<tab>En effet, vu les récentes histoires, c'est préoccupant.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004410_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Elidibus plainly has no need of a new host, so the question becomes, who?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004410_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>On soupçonnait déjà Elidibus d'avoir pris le contrôle du corps de Zenos... Et si un autre Ascien s'était emparé de ce centurio<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004420_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>It may be that another player has joined the game.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004420_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Il pourrait s'agir d'un pion dont nous ignorions l'existence et qui aurait rejoint l'échiquier...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004430_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>Something to consider, at any rate. But come, there is work to be done.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004430_SHADOWHUNTER<tab>C'est en tout cas un autre sujet à creuser. Pour l'heure, nous ferions mieux d'y aller.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004440_ZENOS<tab>These bloodless games make for poor sport.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004440_ZENOS<tab>Évidemment... Ce conflit a perdu de son intérêt...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004450_ZENOS<tab>Mayhap if Father... Nay. I am a stranger to him in this body.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004450_ZENOS<tab>Et mon père... que dis-je, il n'a aucun lien de parenté avec ce corps. Sans doute est-ce pour cela que je ne ressens rien pour lui. Hmm...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004460_ZENOS<tab>Besides, there is but one hand that can make me whole again. My enemy...my friend...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004460_ZENOS<tab>Le seul à me permettre d'être moi-même, c'est lui... Ma proie préférée, mon ami...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004470_ZENOS<tab>Besides, there is but one hand that can make me whole again. My enemy...my friend...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004470_ZENOS<tab>La seule à me permettre d'être moi-même, c'est elle... Ma proie préférée, mon amie...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004480_ZENOS<tab>I know not what entertainment occupies you, but if you will not clear the way for me, then I shall seize the reins of fate once more.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05002_004480_ZENOS<tab>Tu es parti<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> aiguiser tes griffes, et où que tu sois, tu dois être en train de frayer ta propre voie, pas vrai<var 1D /var>? Fort bien... Pendant ce temps, je mettrai mon destin à genoux.
